  "description": "This image depicts two young boys posing outdoors during golden hour. An older boy, possibly in his early teens, is sitting on a low stone wall, partially obscured by a dark jacket worn by a younger boy who is sitting on his lap. The younger boy is looking directly at the camera with a serious expression. The older boy is looking slightly off to the side with a neutral expression. Both boys have red hair. The background features a grassy area with scattered rocks, leading to a distant body of water under a warm, orange and yellow sunset sky. There's a slight haze in the air, contributing to the soft lighting.",
